flowchart TD
    %% Zero-Cost 10/10 Full Stack Architecture Diagram
    
    subgraph Client [Frontend UI / Client]
        UI[Next.js 15 App Router]
        STYLES[Tailwind CSS v4 + shadcn/ui]
        MOTION[Framer Motion]
        UI --- STYLES
        UI --- MOTION
    end

    subgraph API [API & Transport Layer]
        TRPC[tRPC v11 + TanStack Query]
        ZOD[Zod Validation]
        TRPC --- ZOD
    end

    subgraph Server [Backend Compute & Services]
        NEXT_API[Next.js Server / API Routes]
        GO_SRV[Go Microservice / PDF Generator]
        BULLMQ[BullMQ Background Workers]
    end

    subgraph Database [Infrastructure & Data Layer]
        SUPA_DB[(Supabase PostgreSQL)]
        SUPA_AUTH{Supabase Auth & RLS}
        UPSTASH[(Upstash Redis Cache/Queue)]
        STORAGE[Supabase Storage / Assets]
    end

    subgraph Observability [Telemetry & DevOps]
        SENTRY[Sentry Error Tracking]
        POSTHOG[PostHog Product Analytics]
        GITHUB[GitHub Actions CI/CD]
    end

    %% Client to API
    Client <-->|Strict Type-Safe JSON| API
    Client -->|Telemetry Events| Observability
    
    %% API to Server
    API <-->|RPC Calls| NEXT_API
    
    %% Server to DB
    NEXT_API <-->|Prisma Queries| SUPA_DB
    NEXT_API -->|Verify Session| SUPA_AUTH
    NEXT_API <-->|Asset Uploads| STORAGE
    
    %% Async Jobs & Microservices
    NEXT_API -.->|Enqueue Tasks| BULLMQ
    BULLMQ <-->|Queue Storage| UPSTASH
    BULLMQ -.->|Trigger Generation| GO_SRV
    GO_SRV <-->|Raw SQL via sqlc| SUPA_DB
    
    %% Deployment flow
    GITHUB -.->|Automated Builds| Server
